{"title":"我一锨一锨把火烧","authors":["叶枫"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":6,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一锨一锨把火烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶枫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一锨一锨把火烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锅炉底下火苗高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是矿山大心脏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把锅炉好好烧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假若锅炉烧不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电滚不转灯死了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高车断气罐上吊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电箩不唱哑了嗓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风车悄悄睡大觉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一锨一锨把火烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕双手磨起大燎泡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不顾汗流如雨浇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和这个老锅炉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块过活二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的皮气我知道；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火小了气不壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火大了要飞爆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一锨一锨把火烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"添上生炭火兴旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有件喜事心头跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从解放这工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产生管理委员会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我烧火的也选上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经理领导来开会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们坐到一个桌面上。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一锨一锨把火烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工友们说：“当主人翁要当好！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命竞赛劲头高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说啦："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一天节约炭一车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锅炉照样烧的好；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证烧够百篷气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十天给他洗次澡。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一锨一锨把火烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你瞧锅炉肚下闪红光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心操在他身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电滚飞转灯光亮堂堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高车提煤到井上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电箩高兴“咣咣”唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风车呼呼撵风跑。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九、五、于焦作矿区"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}